00:03:29.990 --> 00:03:31.450
Puedes llamarme Lingsha.

00:03:32.320 --> 00:03:34.329
Ling... Lingsha.

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:35.710
No es Linglingsha,

00:03:35.710 --> 00:03:36.590
sino Lingsha.

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:39.310
Lingsha.

00:03:40.030 --> 00:03:42.510
